#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/qmJGd5IfURq8iPQ9KF3les47vFS.jpg" group-title="|FR| FILMS 4K/3D" tvg-type="movie" description="The nightmare isn't over as unstoppable killer Michael Myers escapes from Laurie Strode's trap to continue his ritual bloodbath. Injured and taken to the hospital, Laurie fights through the pain as she inspires residents of Haddonfield, to rise up against Myers. Taking matters into their own hands, the Strode women and other survivors form a vigilante mob to hunt down Michael and end his reign of terror once and for all." year="2021-10-14" director="Miramax, Universal Pictures, Blumhouse Productions, Trancas International Films, Rough House Pictures, Home Again Productions" actors="N/A",FR - Halloween Kills  (2021)
